Concurrency
    Many functions aren't thread safe
    Callback functions
        Concurrent safe
            Exceptions documented
        Must NOT use Application.QueueUpdate*
        Application.Draw called automatically
    Concurrent Primitive access
        Must sync go func() { app.QueueUpdateDraw(primitiveAccessFn) }()
            Application.QueueUpdate
            Application.QueueUpdateDraw
    Concurrent safe
        TextView
            io.Writer
                MUST use TextView.SetChangedFunc to redraw
        Application
            Draw
                Can DEADLOCK if you call it from the main thread
                    e.g. in a callback function of a widget
    Misc
        TextView
            SetChangedFunc
                useful with concurrent io.Writer
                    writes won't refresh the screen
                        use this handler to refresh
                rules
                    CAN call Application.Draw
                    CAN call TextView.HasFocus
                    Access to any other variables
                        from this primitive
                            or any other primitive
                        MUST use
                            Application.QueueUpdate
